550
00:43:12,780 --> 00:43:13,960
Hứa đi!

551
00:43:15,900 --> 00:43:17,530
Tôi hứa, Laura.

552
00:43:17,580 --> 00:43:21,580
Tôi xin lỗi.

553
00:43:23,700 --> 00:43:25,580
